data.title: 1:18 scale 1963 Lotus 25 Jim Clark #8 Italian Grand Prix
data.meta_description: 1:18 scale 1963 Lotus 25 Jim Clark #8, Italian Grand Prix winner. Limited Edition 1 of 500 This is the Lotus 25 in which Jim Clark won his very first Formula One World Championship. He won the Championship at Monza, in Italy with three races to spare in 1963 and won seven of the ten races in the World Championship. This #8 Lotus 25 is a highly accurate scale model of that fabulous car. This brand new, limited edition model has cockpit, suspension, gearbox and engine detail visible through the covering mesh. This is a ‘kerbside’ model so no bodywork is removable. The model is mounted on a black leatherette base with a plaque detailing the model and comes with a perspex display cover and black outer box. This model is brand new in its original packaging - never opened.
data.text:
Description

1:18 scale 1963 Lotus 25 Jim Clark #8, Italian Grand Prix winner.

Limited Edition 1 of 500

This is the Lotus 25 in which Jim Clark won his very first Formula One World Championship. He won the Championship at Monza, in Italy with three races to spare in 1963 and won seven of the ten races in the World Championship. This #8 Lotus 25 is a highly accurate scale model of that fabulous car.

This brand new, limited edition model has cockpit, suspension, gearbox and engine detail visible through the covering mesh. This is a ‘kerbside’ model so no bodywork is removable. The model is mounted on a black leatherette base with a plaque detailing the model and comes with a perspex display cover and black outer box.

This model is brand new in its original packaging - never opened.
